description: This source file implements a platform-dependent utility function for creating an Object Array component in the Object Array object infrastructure within the BroadWay Service Delivery System. It primarily contains an interface function to create and return an object of type AnscObjectArrayCO.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE AnscCreateObjectArrayComponent(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates and returns a new Object Array component handle using the platform-dependent factory function AnscObjectArrayCOCreate.
